data.eml:eml: Two new species of Philosepedon Eaton (Diptera: Psychodidae: Psychodinae) from the Atlantic Coastal Rain Forest of northeastern Brazil

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Bravo, Freddy, Chagas, Cinthia, Cordeiro, Danilo (2006): Two new species of Philosepedon Eaton (Diptera: Psychodidae: Psychodinae) from the Atlantic Coastal Rain Forest of northeastern Brazil. Zootaxa 1206: 63-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.172396
